body_html:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/cmake/README.md talks about known-good configurations, but I'm pretty sure we build with VS 2015 Update 3 regularly.

Perhaps the introduction of DT_COMPLEX support in 88a6cde has broken the GPU build on Windows?

body:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/cmake/README.md talks about known-good configurations, but I'm pretty sure we build with VS 2015 Update 3 regularly. 

Perhaps the introduction of DT_COMPLEX support in https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/88a6cdeb5ee79765462932a611d4d16dd715007c has broken the GPU build on Windows?
